#: ../../source/mp/operator.rst:162
msgid ""
"**ConfigMap mount** -- The ``$(cat ...)`` pattern reads the connection "
"JSON inline.  The ConfigMap name is always ``<LMCacheEngine "
"name>-connection``."
msgstr "**ConfigMap 挂载** -- ``$(cat ...)`` 模式以内联方式读取连接 JSON。ConfigMap 名称始终为 ``<LMCacheEngine name>-connection``\\ 。"

